metadata.name: Wahala
metadata.description:
When she looks at you and you loose total control of your senses and it seems like you are staring into space.

After Purchase a canvas print of 60*80 cm will be shipped to the owner anywhere on the planet.

The owner of this Piece gets access to
The Original Photograph,
The Project Files of the song,(Stems, .wav and FLP) if they so wish
A life time Ticket to Music Performances by Hi_Ceejay,
A Lifetime Ticket to Art Exhibitions by Danekumo,
In Virtual and in Real life &

Access to Hi_Ceejay's Discord, which means access to Hi_Ceejays Music and Art, a week before release for the entire year of 2022
